OL,3,CPolice use nasal spray to save
OL,4,Ccollapsed woman's life
OL,6,FPolice in South Yorkshire saved a
OL,7,Fwoman's life by using a nasal spray
OL,8,Fnow being routinely carried by some
OL,9,Fofficers.
OL,11,FThe woman was found collapsed in
OL,12,FSheffield city centre by officers on
OL,13,Fpatrol on Friday.
OL,15,FSgt Simon Pickering, who noticed the
OL,16,Fwoman, said she failed to respond to
OL,17,Finitial attempts to revive her.
OL,19,FBut he was carrying the spray Naloxone
OL,20,Fas part of an initiative announced
OL,21,Flast month.
