OL,3,CPolice use nasal spray to save
OL,4,Ccollapsed woman's life
OL,6,FSgt Pickering said the woman began to
OL,7,Fcome round within five minutes of
OL,8,Freceiving the nasal spray. He and a
OL,9,Fcolleague stayed with her until
OL,10,Fparamedics arrived.
OL,12,F"Administering the Naloxone stopped
OL,13,Fher from going into cardiac arrest and
OL,14,Fpotentially saved her life," Sgt
OL,15,FPickering said.
OL,17,F"I was really impressed by the
OL,18,Fresponse of Naloxone and it was very
OL,19,Funintrusive as it works as a nasal
OL,20,Fspray."
