OL,3,CPolice use nasal spray to save
OL,4,Ccollapsed woman's life
OL,6,FThe spray, which is being used by
OL,7,Fpolice forces across the UK, helps to
OL,8,Freverse the effects of overdoses from
OL,9,Fdrugs like heroin and morphine, as
OL,10,Fwell as substances including
OL,11,Fmethadone, fentanyl and Nitazenes.
OL,13,FIt comes after there were a record
OL,14,F5,448 drug-related deaths in England
OL,15,Fand Wales in 2023.
OL,17,FDet Ch Insp Mark Oughton, of South
OL,18,FYorkshire Police, said: "As police
OL,19,Fofficers, our overriding priority is
OL,20,Fto save and preserve lives, and
OL,21,FNaloxone does just that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
