OL,3,CPolice use nasal spray to save
OL,4,Ccollapsed woman's life
OL,6,F"As shown by this incident,
OL,7,Fadministering it buys crucial time for
OL,8,Fmedical intervention by paramedics and
OL,9,Fhospital staff. Had Naloxone not been
OL,10,Fgiven to this woman when it was, she
OL,11,Fcould have fallen into cardiac arrest."
